  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I [INAUDIBLE] tell you if it was one week or two weeks, I just couldn't, but I believe that it was very short time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rosa [? will ?] in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have not any-- any knowledge what was going to-- to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was going as well, I will have to tell you the story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very short.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we have, as I told you that last-- very, [INAUDIBLE] time, we have been working together, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The workers-- there was no production, so we have-- social-- social with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was working with my wife, who had been very distressed, you know, because-- I have a belief that when somebody is to Auschwitz to go, or-- I have a belief that we are-- that we are sent to Gross Rosen, that we are going for a-- there's only luck, but then nothing sure with with it.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had been distressed, and Schindler was passing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, he approached us, and he asked, when you have some valuable, you have to-- I would take it and I will give it back to in Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I believe he he he goes by the idea that we are well off, because I was very close to Mr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Bankier.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On first-name, and so on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bankier has a very well-off people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was supposed to be one of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did he believe that we haven't got needs?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Whatever I said was, bread, we were dying, the bread, and I put it in a boxes, where the ammunition was supposed to be, two or three boxes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before my wife arrived, I ate everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You ate--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I ate everything what what I sent.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
